### Now type in ping google.com
- We type in ping google.com into the terminal.

-Now Ping uses ICMP(Internet Control Message Protocol) to test the performance of the connect and speed between devices to see if the connection is safe.

-The time messured between connected devices is measured in ping, the measuring is done using ICMP's echo packet and then ICMP's echo reply from the target device.
